duct with the University  contact  Michael Diaz  Title IX Coordinator nAmy Truelove  Deputy Title IX Coordinator nDanielle Earls  Deputy Title IX Coordinator nOffice for Access and Equity n    S Marshfield Ave  M C     n               nTitleIX uic edu nhttp   oae uic edu sexual misconduct report an incident  TitleIX uic edu http   oae uic edu sexual misconduct report an incident  For more information about reporting options and resources  visit  nhttp   sexualmisconduct uic edu http   sexualmisconduct uic edu A report of sexual misconduct may also be filed with  Chicago Office  Office for Civil Rights nU S  Department of Education nCitigroup Center n    W  Madison Street  Suite      nChicago  IL           n                nOCR Chicago ed gov nFAX                nTDD               OCR Chicago ed gov UIC Complaint Resolution Procedure  Title IX Investigation UIC Complaint Resolution Procedure  Student Conduct Process Sexual Misconduct Sexual Misconduct  n nBack to main content n n n n n n Back to main content Rights and Options Sexual Misconduct Policy Coverage and Definitions Report an Incident Resources Policies and Procedures  n nUIC Logo n n n n UIC Logo  n          Office for Access and Equity n         Helpful Links Office of Diversity Disability Resource Center Human Resources Dean of Students Campus Advocacy Network UIC Police Contact               oae uic edu Social Media Accounts UIC edu links UIC edu Academic Calendar Athletics Campus Directory Disability Resources Emergency Information Event Calendar Job Openings Library Maps UIC Today UI Health Veterans Affairs Privacy Statement Campuses University of Illinois System Urbana Champaign Springfield Cookie Settings 